  window.renderUsers=function(){const b=byId('usersBody');if(!b)return;const q=val('userSearchV10700').toLowerCase(),rf=val('userRoleFilterV10700'),sf=val('userStatusFilterV10700');const rows=(window.data?.users||[]).filter(u=>{const s=u.status||(u.is_active===false?'suspended':'active');return(!q||[u.full_name,u.username,u.email,u.phone].some(v=>String(v||'').toLowerCase().includes(q)))&&(!rf||legacyRoleMap(u.role_key||u.role)===rf)&&(!sf||s===sf);});b.innerHTML=rows.map(u=>{const s=u.status||(u.is_active===false?'suspended':'active'),role=securityDataV10700.roles.find(r=>String(r.role_key||r.id)===String(legacyRoleMap(u.role_key||u.role)));return `<tr><td><div class="user-card-name"><b>${esc(u.full_name||'-')}</b><small>@${esc(u.username||'-')} · ${esc(u.email||u.phone||'')}</small></div></td><td>${esc(u.department_name||'-')}<br><small>${esc(u.job_title||'-')}</small></td><td><span class="badge">${esc(role?.name||userRoleLabel(u.role))}</span></td><td><span class="status-pill status-${s}">${statusLabel(s)}</span></td><td>${esc(u.last_login_at?new Date(u.last_login_at).toLocaleString('ar-SA'):'لم يسجل')}</td><td><span class="perm-scope-badge">${esc(u.scope_type||'all')}</span></td><td class="row-actions"><button onclick="openAdvancedUserForm(${u.id})">تعديل</button><button class="light" onclick="copyUserPermissionsV10700(${u.id})">نسخ الصلاحيات</button><button class="light" onclick="toggleUserStatusV10700(${u.id},'${s}')">${s==='active'?'إيقاف':'إعادة تفعيل'}</button><button class="light" onclick="endUserSessionsV10700(${u.id})">إنهاء الجلسات</button></td></tr>`}).join('')||'<tr><td colspan="7">لا توجد نتائج</td></tr>';const users=window.data?.users||[];if(byId('permKpiUsers'))byId('permKpiUsers').textContent=users.length;if(byId('permKpiActive'))byId('permKpiActive').textContent=users.filter(u=>(u.status||(u.is_active===false?'suspended':'active'))==='active').length;if(byId('permKpiSuspended'))byId('permKpiSuspended').textContent=users.filter(u=>u.is_active===false||u.status==='suspended').length;if(byId('permKpiSessions'))byId('permKpiSessions').textContent=securityDataV10700.sessions.filter(s=>s.is_active!==false).length;if(byId('permKpiSensitive'))byId('permKpiSensitive').textContent=users.filter(u=>Object.keys(safeJson(u.permissions)).some(k=>SENSITIVE.has(k.split('.').pop()))).length;};
  window.toggleUserStatusV10700=async function(id,s){if(!requirePermissionV10700('users.manage'))return;const next=s==='active'?'suspended':'active';if(!confirm(next==='suspended'?'سيتم إيقاف المستخدم ومنع دخوله. متابعة؟':'إعادة تفعيل المستخدم؟'))return;const r=await sb.from('app_users').update({status:next,is_active:next==='active',updated_at:new Date().toISOString()}).eq('id',id);if(r.error)return msg(r.error.message,'err');if(next==='suspended')await endUserSessionsV10700(id,true);await auditV10700('users.status','users',id,s,next);await refreshAll();renderUsers();};
